						<p class="text-gray-600">Define and manage variables that can be updated in real-time based on your business logic.</p>
					</div>
					<div class="text-center">
						<div class="mb-4 flex justify-center">
							<svg class="w-12 h-12 text-gray-700" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
